  "texts": [
    "This can help them understand the rationale behind the reform and equip them with the necessary skills and knowledge to effectively implement it. 2.",
    "Adequate resources: Ensuring that schools have access to sufficient resources, including teaching materials, equipment, and infrastructure, is essential for the success of the reform.",
    "The Education Bureau can play a role in allocating resources and providing support to schools that are in need.",
    "Collaboration with local communities, businesses, and organizations can also help in securing additional resources. 3.",
    "Evaluation and assessment: Developing appropriate evaluation and assessment mechanisms is crucial to monitor the progress and effectiveness of the reform."
  ]
